df = df.reset_index(drop=True)

enc = preprocessing.OneHotEncoder()
df2 = pd.DataFrame(enc.fit_transform(df[['diag_1']]).toarray())
df2.columns = enc.get_feature_names()

df3 = pd.DataFrame(enc.fit_transform(df[['diag_2']]).toarray())
df3.columns = enc.get_feature_names()

df4 = pd.DataFrame(enc.fit_transform(df[['diag_3']]).toarray())
df4.columns = enc.get_feature_names()



tmp = df2 + df3 + df4

for col in tmp.columns:
    tmp[col] = tmp[col].replace(2, 1)
    tmp[col] = tmp[col].replace(3, 1)
        
        
df = pd.concat([df, tmp], axis=1)
df = df.drop(columns=['diag_1', 'diag_2', 'diag_3'])
